manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Perfect baskets for organizing & cutting down on clutter, these collapsible cubes add functionality to your cube storage shelf! These 11 inch storage bins easily side in and pull out of cube storage shelves thanks to their sewn-in handles. They are an unbeatable cube of color, organization, & style.

Sorbus shelf storage bins are both durable and easy to use, these Collapsible Storage Cubes are a terrific choice! Store anything from toys on the shelves, below a coffee table top, or on an office desk to laundry inside these sturdy and flexible cubes with bright colors and strong handles.

Making Storage Easy The collapsible design assembles in seconds and folds flat. Create a functional kid's play area where Legos, books, & stuffed animals have a cozy cube to call home. Bins are lightweight, sturdy, & easy for kids to place on the floor to grab their favorite toy. When not in use, slide them underneath a bench or back inside your cube organizer stand until the next play date. These bins also transform a closet/laundry room when filled with linens, clothes, seasonal items, holiday ornaments, & more.

The Possibilities Are Endless! Organizing baskets for shelves useful for wrangling household items to collecting unruly toys, camouflage and conceal some of the most common household eyesores. Try simple storage with lightweight bins that make a practical, attractive addition to any room. Bins complement cube storage organizer shelves & provide adequate space to sort your clutter. Our basket bins are made of nonwoven polypropylene and cardboard with colorful lightweight fabric. A side handle allows for easy transportation.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These bins were the perfect fit for my shelf unit!! I l've bought similar bins before (various brands) and they never seemed true to size & seemed very thinly made & flimsy. NOT THESE! These are absolutely true to size & seem extremely sturdy! They fit perfectly, are a beautiful assortment of colors that look so nice. Each bin has a decent size handle making it easy to pull the bin in & out. Each bin holds a good amount of stuff in it & is not "saggy" when you are holding the bin with things in it. They come nicely packaged, securely wrapped & boxed & they are odor free when you open up the sealed wrapping around them. I like them so much I have bought another box of them already. I 🩷 the high quality of this item at a price that is affordable. I'm sure I'll be getting more of these in the near future. Highly satisfied customer!
